Title: barcelo-residences-dubai-marina
Post Content: Situated in Dubai, 1.4 km from The Walk at JBR, Barceló Residences Dubai Marina features accommodation with free WiFi, a garden, and access to a hot tub and a fitness room. Each unit is fully fitted with a washing machine, a flat-screen TV, a sofa and desk. There is also a kitchen in all of the units equipped with an oven and a fridge. Barceló Residences Dubai Marina offers an outdoor pool. is Dubai International Airport, 33 km from the property. Couples particularly like the location — they rated it 8.6 for a two-person trip. Hotel chain/brand: Barceló Hotels & Resorts
Location: Dubai Marina, Dubai, United Arab Emirates
